<h1>RectangleDanceParty</h1>
<div class="center-box">
    <p>A rectangle with stylishness set to <em>none</em>
        will move very quickly and ungracefully.
        A rectangle with stylishness set to <em>some</em>
        will move slightly less quickly.
        A rectangle with stylishness set to <em>very</em>
        will move slowly and gracefully.</p>
    <p><strong>Hover over a rectangle to let it know
        it's being watched. Nobody likes dancing while being
        watched.</strong></p>
    <div id="wrap">
        <div id="disp-box">
            <% @person.find_each do |pe| %>
                <% wght = (pe.weight.to_i - (pe.name.length + 15))/5 %>
                <% hght = (pe.height.to_i * 1.4) %>
                <% if wght < 5 %>
                    <% wght = 5 %>
                <% end %>
                <% if hght < 5 %>
                    <% hght = 5 %>
                <% end %>
                <div class="<%=pe.color%> <%=pe.stylishness%>" style="padding-right:<%=wght%>px;padding-bottom:<%=hght%>px"><%=pe.name%><br><span class="stil">(<%=pe.stylishness%>)</span></div>
            <% end %>
        </div>
    </div>
    <p class="stil">If the rectangles refuse to dance, you may need to
        refresh the page. üêµ</p>
    <div class="btns">
        <%= link_to 'People', controller: 'people' %>
    </div>
</div>
